    "您的 API Key 将使用最高安全级别加密存储在您设备的 Keychain （钥匙串）中，绝不会上传至任何服务器。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your API Key is encrypted and stored securely in your device's Keychain. It will never be uploaded to any server."
